title: 820-2879 fan snip no boot
message: howdy howdy, from the bottom of the pile, I've got this sucker. no signs of liquid damage, pin 11 of j5100 was burnt off but that's all the damage I can see. mcp_pwrg. beep with no ram, silent with ram, usb mouse no light, mcp_ps_pwrgd present, no spi_mlb_clk.

title: 820-2879 fan snip no boot
message: Yeah, usually a bad MCP in these, not worth the effort.
